content: Folder <1>{{folderName}}</1> is located in the password-protected folder. Please enter a password for the folder

comment.text: This key displays a message indicating a folder is password-protected and prompts the user to enter the password. It appears within a password form, likely in a dialog or panel, to unlock access to a specific folder. The `folderName` value will be replaced with the name of the folder being accessed.
